<h3 id="flip-a-coin">Flip a Coin</h3>
<p>[demo:ex:1]</p>
<p>Make a program that simulates flipping a coin \(N\) times. Print out &quot;tail&quot; or &quot;head&quot; for each flip and let the program count the number of heads.</p>
